---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Enam Amevo" currentPage="about">
  <div class="about-page">

    <div class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-photo">
        <img src="/assets/img/headshot.jpg" alt="Enam Amevo" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-intro">
        <h1 class="heading">About Me</h1>
        <p class="about-tagline">"Go beyond the impossible and kick reason to the curb!"<br><span class="quote-attr">— Kamina, Tengen Toppa Gurren Lagann</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Who I Am</h2>
        <p>
          I'm Enam Amevo, a first-generation American with roots in Togo, a small country in West Africa. As the eldest of three sisters, I've always felt a responsibility to lead by example and push boundaries. I grew up attending IB schools, and the learner profiles I internalized there shaped me into someone who's endlessly curious and driven to grow every single day.
        </p>
        <p>
          Outside of engineering, I'm deeply into anime, film, music, history, psychology, comic books, and sitcoms. I don't think being a great engineer means shrinking the rest of who you are. The creativity I pull from storytelling and art directly fuels how I think about design problems. My goal has always been to bring both intellect and creativity to everything I build.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>What I Do</h2>
        <p>
          I'm a 3rd year Electrical Engineering student at the Georgia Institute of Technology, with threads in Circuit Technology and Signal Processing, and a minor in Materials Science & Biomedical Engineering. My focus is on integrated system design: bridging the gap between analog/mixed-signal circuits, digital logic and VLSI, and low-level embedded software.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm a member of SiliconJackets, where I work on the Analog/Mixed-Signal team designing circuits in the Sky130 PDK using Cadence Virtuoso. I also participate in a VIP research project studying 6502 and 65c816 processor architectures and exploring XMOS multicore microcontrollers. This summer, I'll be joining Marvell Technology as an SoC Integration RTL Intern.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <div class="edu-card">
          <div class="edu-header">
            <h3>Georgia Institute of Technology</h3>
            <span class="edu-date">Expected December 2027</span>
          </div>
          <p class="edu-degree">B.S. Electrical Engineering</p>
          <p class="edu-details">Threads: Circuit Technology, Signal Processing</p>
          <p class="edu-details">Minor: Materials Science & Engineering</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <div class="about-skills">
          <span class="tag">SystemVerilog/Verilog</span>
          <span class="tag">VHDL</span>
          <span class="tag">C/C++</span>
          <span class="tag">CUDA/MPI</span>
          <span class="tag">MATLAB</span>
          <span class="tag">Cadence/Synopsys</span>
          <span class="tag">PCB Design</span>
          <span class="tag">FPGA</span>
          <span class="tag">Sky130 PDK</span>
          <span class="tag">XMOS</span>
          <span class="tag">Embedded Systems</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>What Drives Me</h2>
        <p>
          I want to impact the fields of computing, healthcare, energy, and even film and television through electrical engineering. I believe deeply in the intersection of technical skill and creative vision. This website is a living record of that journey, from coursework and research to personal projects and everything in between. I can, and will, have it all.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 40px 80px;
  }

  .about-hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 4px solid #ffca8a;
  }

  .about-photo {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .about-photo img {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 4px solid #c2c2c2;
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .about-intro .heading {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    display: block;
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-tagline {
    font-family: 'retro1', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #74808a;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .quote-attr {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #a0a0a0;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .about-content {
    font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
    color: #374054;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #374054;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #f0f0f0;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .edu-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 4px solid #c2c2c2;
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .edu-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .edu-header h3 {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #374054;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .edu-date {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
    font-size: 0.45rem;
    color: #a0a0a0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .edu-degree {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }

  .edu-details {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #74808a;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }

  .about-skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page { padding: 40px 20px 60px; }
    .about-hero {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>